Description: This luxurious leather case features a sleek and compact, Fly-Through Checkpoint-Friendly design and shiny, silver-toned hardware, and it's available in several colors. It has a top zip closure, and it boasts a roomy, lined interior with a padded, removable laptop computer sleeve; a center zip section; plenty of space for your files; and an organizer section with card slots, pen sleeves, a key leash, and slide pockets. Two front pockets with turn-lock closures offer quick access to frequently-needed items, and the McKlein USA Verona - Ladies' Fly-Through Checkpoint-Friendly Laptop Briefcase comes with double shoulder straps for your carrying comfort. Two small front pockets with magnetic snaps. Front and back pocket for files. Main compartment divided by secure zipper pocket. Built-in padded laptop sleeve that fits laptops up to 15.4”. Interior organizer section for business cards, pens, keys, cell phones and notepads.
